snippet.title: Kikansha Thomas - Kokugo Sansuu Eigo Playthrough Part 1: Thomas
snippet.description:
Here's a playthrough of one of the exclusive Thomas & Friends games released only in Japan. I'll be covering 4 of the modes with each character, starting with Thomas.

Be aware, that the mode with the Japanese Alphabet has some savestates being utilized since I don't know Japanese all that well, so you can't really blame me on that one. :P

Twitter: https://twitter.com/MH1994_
